{
  "text": "Then Yahweh in an attempt to correct what he saw as what I might call a mistake, no, you don't want to call it that. Started 3,300 years ago with the positive philosophy. Were both the Orion and the Awe philosophies impressed telepathically or were there other techniques used? I am rack. There were two other techniques used one by the entity no longer called Yahweh, who still felt that if it could raise up entities which were superior to the negative forces that these superior entities could spread the law of one. Thus this entity Yod He Ashin Va He came among your people in form according to incarnate a being and mated in the normal reproductive manner of your physical complexes, thus birthing a generation of much larger beings. These beings called Anak, the other method used to a greater effect later in the scenario, as you would call it, was the thought form such as we often use among your peoples to suggest the mysterious or the sublime. You may be familiar with some of these appearances.",
